        </div>

        <center>
            <a href="<%= bidUrl %>" class="button">View Bid Details</a>
        </center>

        <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Monitor your email for updates about this bid</li>
            <li>You can manage your bids from your <a href="https://iptruck.com/dashboard">dashboard</a></li>
            <li>If accepted, coordinate directly with the shipper for details</li>
        </ul>

